[normal]2.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Improving public health outcomes is critical and Nuffield Health is uniquely 
[normal]positioned as a Third Sector 
[normal]organisation
[normal] to achieve long-term, scalable, and leading-edge innovations across the UK healthcare sector. No other healthcare group can combine the freedom to act solely in the interests of the public, with the ability to deli
[normal]ver across a range of services, and the flexibility to take a panoramic view. Our carefully built and managed financial strength permits us to 
[normal]utilise
[normal] the benefits and independence endowed by our not-for-profit status to consider and meet the genuine needs
[normal] of the UK health consumer.
