[normal]13% of our revenue comes from products and services that are less than £1 per day, and approximately 20% of our revenues are p
[normal]rovided from services that are free at the point of delivery – predominately from NHS contracts. We also offer free hea
[normal]lthcare education to the public
[normal] and 
[normal]hold over 650 events 
[normal]annually.
