[normal]We are proud to have been a catalyst in the wellbeing revolution that 
[normal]emphasises
[normal] prevention as much as cure. We have acted on this insight and now inform, inspire and enable people to choose lifestyles that are better for their health and wellbeing. Thi
[normal]s is particularly vital in the workplace where so many days are spent. Our workplace employee fitness and wellbeing 
[normal]centres
[normal] allow people to step directly from work into health.
[normal]46.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Preventative healthcare is central to the viability of the UK’s future. It cont
[normal]ributes to containing sector costs, improves productivity and helps people to take control of their health. Our commitment to this concept is 
[normal]realised
[normal] through our investment in fitness and wellbeing 
[normal]centres
[normal], nutritional therapists, health mentors and physi
[normal]otherapists, as well as in leading-edge digital innovations such as our 
[normal]HealthScore
[normal]™ app. 
[normal]47.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Over the past decade we have acquired four major corporate and fitness chains. We transformed and united them under Nuffield Health to create a unique network of pre
[normal]ventative care for the country. This is our vision made tangible to the people we are here to help.
